

 
This is an Android demo application for displaying the latest popular  Instagram Photos using the Instagram API. 

Time spent: 4-5 hours spent in total

Completed user stories:
     
  1. User can scroll through current popular photos from Instagram
  2. For each photo displayed, user can see the following details:

      Graphic, Caption, Username
     

Notes:

Spent some time making the UI work across multiple phone resolutions by playing around with the RelativeLayout.Sometime for 
Checking API (JSON data) and CustomerAdapterView
